程序包 Model

类 ChatResponse

java.lang.Object
Model.ChatResponse
public class ChatResponse extends Object
Represents a response from an AI chat service in the Smart Finance Application. This class encapsulates metadata about the response, including its identifier, object type, creation timestamp, model used, and a list of response choices.
版本:
1.0
作者:
Group 19
